ARM: OMAP2+: DRA7: Add hwmod entries for PWMSS

Add hwmod entries for the PWMSS on DRA7.

Set l4_root_clk_div as the main_clk of PWMSS. It is fixed-factored clock
equal to L4PER2_L3_GICLK/2(l3_iclk_div/2).

